                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 367.54/18.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Swiss Legation</gloss> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Department of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <dateline>
                    <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-content" calendar="gregorian"
                        when="1915-03-04">undated</date>
                </dateline>
                <p rend="center">[Undated memorandum received March 4, 1915.]</p>
                <p>In view of the Cabinet of Washington having accepted the protection of Swiss
                    citizens in Turkey who make such application to the representatives of the
                    United States, and in view of the events at the Dardanelles, please make sure
                    that our compatriots will receive the same protection as Americans.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
